        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">Weak fit:</span>{' '}
          {lensWeakFitLine}
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">Tradeoff:</span> {lensTradeoffLine}
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-zinc-500">
        Full evidence detail lives in{' '}
        <a href="#verdict" class="text-hunt-500 hover:text-hunt-400">
          Why This Verdict
        </a>
        .
      </p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500">
        Best fit, weak fit, and tradeoff summarize the linked evidence.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6 rounded-xl border border-zinc-700 bg-zinc-900 p-4 shadow-sm" aria-label="Reader controls">
